{"tid":1153261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"殺豬電壓低未暈已放血　港府被促提高撲殺透明度","createTime":"2019-05-13T13:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T17:12:50.000Z","uid":17646,"like":5,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7b7df7088939d25323d619b2301e3484b502510f","tid":1153261,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:27:40.000Z","msg":"港府因應爆發非洲豬瘟今日(13日)起撲殺上水屠房6000隻活豬，有關注動物權益的團體要求政府提高撲殺透明度，改善動物福利，促請食物及衞生局局長陳肇始交代是否違法虐畜。 <br />\n<br />\n團體「救救港豬」代表指，無論豬隻由內地運送至上水屠房，又或政府與業界拉鋸期間，牠們都沒有食物，僅有少量水飲，加上昨天(12日)集會期間用6隻豬作為示威工具，要牠們在烈日下暴曬，完全不顧及動物福利，加上撲殺行動透明度低，外界未能知道整個過程。 <br />\n<br />\n代表又批評香港電擊豬隻的電壓，較英國人道屠宰協會建議「不少於250伏特」為低，豬隻未暈低便開始放血，非常殘忍，要求政府提高撲殺透明度。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190513/photo/bkn-20190513161759658-0513_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190513185800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190513%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190513161759658-0513_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190513185800&h=6f458a70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cdde4c5e4706204f10418ab95644c13206ebd618","tid":1153261,"uid":15880,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:29:23.000Z","msg":"救救港豬唔係應該要打擊樓價咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d75a143df478063dfe4e820f507b5da68baee63","tid":1153261,"uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T13:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IB80UV4xw3ZWnNOzWBh4yw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTQwO2g9ODUz/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/d32ff1320c0420ece8ec35a3b74f1f10\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIB80UV4xw3ZWnNOzWBh4yw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTQwO2g9ODUz%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fd32ff1320c0420ece8ec35a3b74f1f10&h=07c857e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點呀動物撚<br />\n殺豬又要理 電有幾殘忍呀<br